<section id="service" class="py-28 sm:py-36 bg-white relative overflow-hidden -mt-px">
	<div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-96 h-96 bg-brand-50 rounded-full blur-[120px] opacity-40" aria-hidden="true"></div>
	<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative">
		<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center mb-20" data-animate="fade-up">
			<div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full border border-brand-200 bg-brand-50 mb-6">
				<span class="text-xs font-bold tracking-widest text-brand uppercase">Service</span>
			</div>
			<h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 tracking-tight leading-tight">
				サービス<span class="text-brand">内容</span>
			</h2>
			<p class="mt-6 text-lg text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">
				Mac Mini の環境構築からセキュリティまで、ワンストップで対応します。
			</p>
		</div>
		<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6" data-animate="fade-up" data-animate-stagger>
			<div class="group relative bg-white rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 hover:border-brand/30 p-8 transition-shadow duration-500 hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-brand/5 hover:-translate-y-1">
				<span class="absolute top-6 right-6 text-5xl font-extrabold text-slate-100 group-hover:text-brand-50 transition-colors">01</span>
				<div class="relative z-10">
					<div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl bg-brand-50 text-brand flex items-center justify-center mb-5 group-hover:bg-brand group-hover:text-white transition-all duration-300">
						<svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2" ry="2"/><path d="M8 21h8M12 17v4"/></svg>
					</div>
					<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">環境構築</h3>
					<p class="text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">
						Mac Miniの初期設定から業務に必要なアプリケーションの導入、ネットワーク設定まで、すぐに業務を開始できる状態にセットアップします。
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="group relative bg-white rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 hover:border-brand/30 p-8 transition-shadow duration-500 hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-brand/5 hover:-translate-y-1">
				<span class="absolute top-6 right-6 text-5xl font-extrabold text-slate-100 group-hover:text-brand-50 transition-colors">02</span>
				<div class="relative z-10">
					<div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl bg-brand-50 text-brand flex items-center justify-center mb-5 group-hover:bg-brand group-hover:text-white transition-all duration-300">
						<svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="11" width="18" height="11" rx="2" ry="2"/><path d="M7 11V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v4"/></svg>
					</div>
					<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">セキュリティ設定</h3>
					<p class="text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">
						ファイアウォール、ディスク暗号化、アクセス制御など、企業レベルのセキュリティ設定を施し、安全な業務環境を実現します。
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>
